'''昌迪加尔政治中心建筑群'''（Chandigarh Capitol Complex；）位于[[印度|印度]][[昌迪加尔|昌迪加尔]]，是建筑师[[勒·柯布西耶|勒·柯布西耶]]设计的政治中心建筑群<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.indianexpress.com/news/le-corbusiers-capitol-complex-a-mess-in-dire-need-of-facelift/760264/0 |title= Le Corbusier's Capitol Complex a mess, in dire need of facelift |work= indianexpress.com |access-date= 2020-11-15 |archive-date= 2013-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131127083613/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/le-corbusiers-capitol-complex-a-mess-in-dire-need-of-facelift/760264/0 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，已列为[[联合国教科文组织|联合国教科文组织]][[世界遗产|世界遗产]]。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/chandigarh-s-capitol-complex-is-now-a-unesco-heritage-site-all-you-need-to-know/story-B3hHy2vXiepSGyM5uXVOYJ.html |title= Chandigarh's Capitol Complex is now a UNESCO heritage site |accessdate= 18 July 2016 |archive-date= 2016-07-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160719125628/http://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/chandigarh-s-capitol-complex-is-now-a-unesco-heritage-site-all-you-need-to-know/story-B3hHy2vXiepSGyM5uXVOYJ.html |dead-url= yes }}</ref> 

==历史==
它占地约100英亩，包括三座建筑：[[议会大厦_(昌迪加尔)|议会大厦]]（Palace of Assembly）、[[秘书处大楼_(昌迪加尔)|秘书处大楼]]（Secretariat Building）和高等法院（High Court），以及四座纪念碑：[[开掌纪念碑|开掌纪念碑]]（Open Hand Monument）、几何山（Geometric Hill）、光影之塔（Tower of Shadows）和烈士纪念碑（Martyrs Monument），以及一个湖泊。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/chandigarh-s-capitol-complex-is-now-a-unesco-heritage-site-all-you-need-to-know/story-B3hHy2vXiepSGyM5uXVOYJ.html |title= Chandigarh’s Capitol Complex is now a UNESCO heritage site: All you need to know |date= 18 July 2016 |work= hindustantimes.com |access-date= 2020-11-15 |archive-date= 2016-07-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160719125628/http://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/chandigarh-s-capitol-complex-is-now-a-unesco-heritage-site-all-you-need-to-know/story-B3hHy2vXiepSGyM5uXVOYJ.html |dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.indianexpress.com/news/capitol-complex-as-le-corbusier-wanted-it/635844/ |title= Capitol Complex, as Le Corbusier wanted it, remains incomplete - Indian Express |work= indianexpress.com |access-date= 2020-11-15 |archive-date= 2013-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131127074822/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/capitol-complex-as-le-corbusier-wanted-it/635844 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/the-most-planned-city/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115154045/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/the-most-planned-city/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=UNESCO1>{{cite web |url= http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/buddha-bihar-nalanda-mahavihara-unesco-world-heritage-site-chandigarh/1/717209.html |title= UNESCO approves all 3 Indian nominations for heritage tag |work= intoday.in |access-date= 2020-11-15 |archive-date= 2016-07-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160719134259/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/buddha-bihar-nalanda-mahavihara-unesco-world-heritage-site-chandigarh/1/717209.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=15 July 2016 |agency=UNESCO World Heritage Centre |accessdate=15 July 2016 |language=en |url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/news/1524 |title=Four sites inscribed on UNESCO’s World Heritage List |work=whc.unesco.org |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716131638/https://whc.unesco.org/en/news/1524 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2016年被联合国教科文组织列入世界遗产名录。

